Output demo/out/ui-download-progress.gif

Require bash

Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 960
Set Height 360
Set TypingSpeed 10 ms
Set Padding 18
Set Framerate 20

Type "$HOVEL_DEMO_UI_BIN show download-progress --width 96 --frames 8 --delay 45ms"
Enter
Wait+Screen /installed mock-exploit-session@v0.0.0-example/
Sleep 2000 ms
